for our company's transformation.

520
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:31,440
I will win Rising Star for the company.

521
00:34:31,659 --> 00:34:34,210
But you mustn't let them fool you.

522
00:34:35,510 --> 00:34:37,030
You are something, Qiao Xin.

523
00:34:38,130 --> 00:34:40,300
No one can beat you
at your way with words.

524
00:34:40,630 --> 00:34:42,730
You can completely twist facts.

525
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:46,530
The company has spent so much
to help you change your image.

526
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:50,230
But has You Xing Video
succeeded in transforming?

527
00:34:50,310 --> 00:34:51,370
Mr. Liu.

528
00:34:51,719 --> 00:34:53,530
Have you ever wondered why?

529
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:59,240
It's because Qiao Xin has never focused on
improving her professional skills.

530
00:34:59,380 --> 00:35:00,920
You're obsessed with being the top

531
00:35:01,140 --> 00:35:03,780
and you get rid of anyone
who's a potential competitor.

532
00:35:03,910 --> 00:35:06,940
If the whole company
agrees with your methods,

533
00:35:07,690 --> 00:35:10,170
then I'm glad that I have left.

534
00:35:10,420 --> 00:35:12,050
Instead, you should think carefully.

535
00:35:12,220 --> 00:35:15,210
Who are you
to compete with me in Rising Star?

536
00:35:15,830 --> 00:35:17,310
Qiu Ying, wait a minute.

537
00:35:17,680 --> 00:35:19,040
Would you like to come back?

538
00:35:22,430 --> 00:35:24,160
Represent You Xing in the competition.

539
00:35:24,900 --> 00:35:28,770
If you're willing to come back,
the company will give you full support.

540
00:35:29,470 --> 00:35:30,760
Thank you.

541
00:35:40,110 --> 00:35:41,230
Mr. Liu.

542
00:35:41,790 --> 00:35:44,560
Are you serious about her coming back?

543
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:46,840
You're even making her the ace?

544
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:49,930
Then what about me?
I've done so much for the company.

545
00:35:50,110 --> 00:35:51,250
I...

546
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:53,640
Qiao Xin.

547
00:35:54,730 --> 00:35:56,420
I trained you from day one.

548
00:35:57,460 --> 00:35:59,560
I know everything
you've done for the company.

549
00:36:00,890 --> 00:36:03,260
I hope you can think about this.

550
00:36:03,620 --> 00:36:05,380
How much has the company given you?

551
00:36:14,190 --> 00:36:16,210
[Summer]

552
00:36:31,290 --> 00:36:32,480
Are you sure it's them?

553
00:36:32,610 --> 00:36:34,810
With clear evidences. As you expected.

554
00:36:34,940 --> 00:36:36,530
Call the police then.

555
00:36:44,530 --> 00:36:45,850
What are you doing?

556
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:50,740
I asked you to show your faces
to support other stores.

557
00:36:51,310 --> 00:36:52,410
Is that too much to ask?

558
00:36:52,590 --> 00:36:54,570
All of you giving me excuses.

559
00:36:54,740 --> 00:36:56,240
"No time".

560
00:36:56,810 --> 00:36:58,310
"Busy with training".

561
00:36:59,580 --> 00:37:02,710
Why don't I see all of you
usually working so hard?

562
00:37:06,930 --> 00:37:08,320
I expected it from others,

563
00:37:08,650 --> 00:37:09,750
but Huo Yao.

564
00:37:09,920 --> 00:37:11,510
Who are you to turn it down?

565
00:37:11,680 --> 00:37:13,760
You're not talented enough and you're old.

566
00:37:14,150 --> 00:37:17,270
Your hands won't move faster
even if you train for another century.

567
00:37:18,720 --> 00:37:21,970
How dare you give me excuses?

568
00:37:23,250 --> 00:37:26,430
Mr. Zhao, you're being a little harsh.

569
00:37:26,950 --> 00:37:31,360
It makes sense that we're training harder
as the competition is near.

570
00:37:32,180 --> 00:37:34,560
Besides, Huo Yao
has been in good condition lately.

571
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:37,290
He has always been.

572
00:37:37,550 --> 00:37:39,640
Our former captain often said

573
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:44,200
that Brother Yao could handle pressure
and rarely made mistakes.

574
00:37:54,100 --> 00:37:56,700
Has your eyesight gotten worse?

575
00:37:57,310 --> 00:37:59,240
Then you should get a new pair!

576
00:37:59,380 --> 00:38:01,750
Can't you see your captain
sitting right across you?

577
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:04,390
Why are you mentioning
your former captain?

578
00:38:04,740 --> 00:38:07,610
He has left.
What he said doesn't matter anymore.

579
00:38:13,070 --> 00:38:14,560
You can handle pressure

580
00:38:15,300 --> 00:38:16,600
and rarely make mistakes?

581
00:38:17,590 --> 00:38:22,190
But you still got defeated by Pei Xi
in the closed beta test.

582
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,290
Huo Yao.

583
00:38:26,170 --> 00:38:30,130
What was that lousy performance
during the closed beta test?

584
00:38:30,260 --> 00:38:32,550
Yet you want me to renew your contract?

585
00:38:36,380 --> 00:38:38,360
-What are you doing?
-Yi Xuan.

586
00:38:38,490 --> 00:38:40,780
Stop! What are you trying to do?

587
00:38:43,330 --> 00:38:44,430
Zhao Yang.

588
00:38:45,050 --> 00:38:46,670
You want to frame people?

589
00:38:46,940 --> 00:38:48,520
You got rid of Brother Kong.

590
00:38:48,790 --> 00:38:50,990
It's time I make you pay
for what you've done.

591
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:52,350
What are you saying?

592
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:54,770
This scoundrel fabricated that video.

593
00:38:58,470 --> 00:38:59,480
Nonsense.

594
00:38:59,610 --> 00:39:00,800
You...

595
00:39:01,500 --> 00:39:02,930
He did more than that.

596
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:07,050
He threatened me with renewing
my contract to screw up the game.

597
00:39:07,310 --> 00:39:08,980
So that Handsome Ji leaves Legends.

598
00:39:09,110 --> 00:39:11,530
-Zhao Yang, you scoundrel!
-Stop! Get back here!

599
00:39:11,710 --> 00:39:12,940
What are you doing?

600
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:14,720
You said I'm not talented enough!

601
00:39:15,050 --> 00:39:16,330
You said I'm old!

602
00:39:16,420 --> 00:39:17,470
-You...
-That's right.

603
00:39:17,610 --> 00:39:19,590
I screwed up the game. It was my fault.

604
00:39:19,810 --> 00:39:21,740
It had nothing to do with Handsome Ji.

605
00:39:24,780 --> 00:39:25,920
You people.

606
00:39:26,980 --> 00:39:30,190
Accusing me with no evidence?

607
00:39:30,340 --> 00:39:31,960
Show me proof!

608
00:39:32,570 --> 00:39:34,240
Stop talking if you don't have proof.

609
00:39:34,370 --> 00:39:37,090
How dare you insult a team manager?

610
00:39:37,450 --> 00:39:39,650
I can fire all of you!

611
00:39:42,780 --> 00:39:44,210
I am the captain.

612
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:48,090
No one has the right to punish
my teammates without my permission.

613
00:39:48,850 --> 00:39:50,840
Pei Xi, I'm helping you here.

614
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:53,210
You're helping me?

615
00:39:53,930 --> 00:39:56,320
But I feel that
you're just helping yourself.

616
00:39:56,500 --> 00:39:59,580
Who said my condition for coming
to Legends was being the captain?

617
00:39:59,670 --> 00:40:03,060
Pei Xi, now isn't the time for this.

618
00:40:03,140 --> 00:40:05,520
No, I want to talk about it now.

619
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:10,160
Fine.

620
00:40:11,550 --> 00:40:12,650
Pei Xi.

621
00:40:15,060 --> 00:40:16,840
You know me.

622
00:40:17,530 --> 00:40:24,400
I am capable of bringing you to this team
and kicking you out.

623
00:40:24,620 --> 00:40:27,120
Better think twice
before going against me.

624
00:40:27,300 --> 00:40:29,590
It's not your call to fire anyone.

625
00:40:31,130 --> 00:40:32,180
Mr. Jin.

626
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,770
Someone is leaving today.

627
00:40:34,740 --> 00:40:35,750
Zhao Yang.

628
00:40:36,190 --> 00:40:37,420
You're fired.

629
00:40:41,340 --> 00:40:45,140
No, Mr. Jin. There's a misunderstanding.

630
00:40:45,380 --> 00:40:47,350
Let me explain.

631
00:40:47,850 --> 00:40:52,070
These kids are spewing nonsense.
Don't listen to them.

632
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:54,670
It's true. I...

633
00:40:54,890 --> 00:40:57,750
I would never do such a thing. Am I right?

634
00:40:58,060 --> 00:41:02,150
Think about it.
I've fought beside you for many years.

635
00:41:02,240 --> 00:41:05,100
I've brought in so many sponsors
for the company,

636
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:07,120
which led to the company's achievements.

637
00:41:07,380 --> 00:41:09,190
If you fire me now,

638
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:13,010
the company might lose all those sponsors.

639
00:41:14,550 --> 00:41:16,200
It has nothing to do with you.

640
00:41:16,620 --> 00:41:18,610
Those sponsors are here because of me.

641
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:21,460
Wang Bin has been arrested.

642
00:41:21,730 --> 00:41:23,370
You might be the next.

643
00:41:26,450 --> 00:41:28,340
You can't deny it anymore.

644
00:41:31,240 --> 00:41:32,220
Yes.

645
00:41:32,990 --> 00:41:35,380
I care a lot about Legends'
business operations,

646
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:38,230
but what I want isn't making
endless amounts of money.

647
00:41:38,890 --> 00:41:42,190
What I want is to form
the world's greatest team.

648
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:44,400
Making money isn't my goal.

649
00:41:44,830 --> 00:41:50,110
Those money are for them to create
miracles under a good environment.

650
00:41:54,590 --> 00:41:56,060
Zhao Yang.

651
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:58,310
You've been with me for many years.

652
00:41:59,170 --> 00:42:01,220
But you've gotten so foolish.

653
00:42:03,350 --> 00:42:04,710
Understood.

654
00:42:05,200 --> 00:42:06,250
Mr. Jin.

655
00:42:06,830 --> 00:42:10,980
Thank you for your guidance
all these years.

656
00:42:21,040 --> 00:42:22,750
"The mission of Legends."

657
00:42:23,980 --> 00:42:25,490
"Never giving up."

658
00:42:44,970 --> 00:42:46,170
Brother Kong.

659
00:42:46,380 --> 00:42:47,680
Handsome Ji.

660
00:42:49,240 --> 00:42:51,620
What are you guys doing here
instead of training?

661
00:42:51,790 --> 00:42:52,830
Brother Kong.

662
00:42:53,240 --> 00:42:56,810
We know the things Zhao Yang did to you.

663
00:42:57,290 --> 00:42:58,440
Captain.

664
00:42:59,230 --> 00:43:00,370
Handsome Ji.

665
00:43:00,770 --> 00:43:03,540
We lost the closed beta game
because of me.

666
00:43:03,800 --> 00:43:05,550
It had nothing to do with you.

667
00:43:06,390 --> 00:43:08,560
Mr. Jin knows the truth now.

668
00:43:16,300 --> 00:43:18,630
I'm sorry.

669
00:43:19,820 --> 00:43:23,120
Handsome Ji, if that's not enough,
we can give him a good beating.

670
00:43:23,300 --> 00:43:24,750
It's fine.

671
00:43:26,070 --> 00:43:27,620
It's in the past now.

672
00:43:28,510 --> 00:43:30,290
Don't cause anymore trouble.

673
00:43:31,920 --> 00:43:34,520
I'm doing pretty well here.

674
00:43:35,400 --> 00:43:36,500
No.

675
00:43:36,980 --> 00:43:38,000
Brother Kong.

676
00:43:38,610 --> 00:43:43,170
All of us wish that you can come back
and be our captain again.

677
00:43:44,110 --> 00:43:47,320
All of us feel low-spirited
at training without you.

678
00:43:47,630 --> 00:43:49,470
Plus, you know how Pei Xi is.

679
00:43:50,880 --> 00:43:51,980
Captain.

680
00:43:52,820 --> 00:43:54,140
We need you.

681
00:44:01,880 --> 00:44:03,020
Thank you.

682
00:44:05,130 --> 00:44:07,430
But VNG took me in

683
00:44:08,880 --> 00:44:10,680
when I was at my lowest.

684
00:44:18,920 --> 00:44:20,810
Say something, guys.

685
00:44:28,810 --> 00:44:30,620
Fine. I'll say it.

686
00:44:32,020 --> 00:44:34,940
Brother Kong,
we don't mean to make you a traitor.

687
00:44:35,060 --> 00:44:37,580
We just wish
to get back on the right track.

688
00:44:39,410 --> 00:44:41,440
Don't forget that you promised Captain Gu

689
00:44:42,490 --> 00:44:44,470
that you would lead us
to the championship.

690
00:44:51,780 --> 00:44:53,010
I'm sorry.

691
00:44:53,180 --> 00:44:54,640
My decision is final.

692
00:44:56,530 --> 00:44:58,020
Captain Gu also said

693
00:44:58,240 --> 00:45:01,630
that no matter which team you are in,
you should believe in your teammates.

694
00:45:02,200 --> 00:45:05,420
No matter what kind of opponent you face,
you must do your best.

695
00:45:06,690 --> 00:45:10,520
Therefore, I will do my best
to defeat you all in the competition.

696
00:45:11,050 --> 00:45:12,760
That's the competitive spirit.

697
00:45:14,960 --> 00:45:16,720
All of you are my dearest buddies.

698
00:45:16,940 --> 00:45:20,290
You are also opponents that I respect
in a competition.

699
00:45:28,300 --> 00:45:30,410
So pull yourself together.

700
00:45:34,290 --> 00:45:36,170
I'll see you at the Fall Championship.

701
00:45:44,360 --> 00:45:45,470
Brother Kong.

702
00:45:46,510 --> 00:45:48,320
See you at the Fall Championship.
